      • deleteActions

        public static AylaAPIRequest deleteActions(java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String> actionIDSet,
                                           com.android.volley.Response.Listener<java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String>> successListener,
                                           ErrorListener errorListener)
        Delete actions from the Datum given a list of Action Id's.This lists only deleted the list of Actions whose Id's match the ones passes in parameter actionIDSet. We make sure that these actions already exist in user Datum and deleted only those actions.The response to the updateDatum contains an array of actions that are still in user's datum after the deletion. We then give back the deleted action Id's in the response
        参数:
        actionIDSet - Hashset of action Id's
        successListener - Listener to receive on successful deletion and contains the actions that were deleted
        errorListener - Listener to receive an AylaError should one occur
        返回:
        the AylaAPIRequest object
